m</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\r\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f320560a739192ee930c01576ef74d9ee99df7","tid":1537102,"uid":225968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:52:50.000Z","msg":"快啲幫幫手"}]}